  "description": "A vibrant and dramatic sunset over a body of water, likely a bay or ocean. The sky is ablaze with fiery orange and red hues, streaked with wispy, horizontal clouds that resemble brushstrokes. The colors transition from intense orange near the horizon to deeper reds and purples higher in the sky. Silhouetted against the bright sky is a distant landscape of hills and a faint outline of a bridge or structure. In the foreground, dark green trees and foliage create a contrasting, grounded element. The overall impression is one of grandeur and natural beauty.",
